List of Python functions available in this repository:

Plotting:
-Generating beautiful figures using Seaborn/ matplotlib.pyplot 
-Figure settings for high resolution export and customizing color palette 
-Rastor plot and PSTH 
-Generating 3D plots
-Connectivity graph plots 

Data Preprocessing:
-Binning/reshaping matrix based on mean/sum/average 
-Adding new dimension 
-Normalize and z-score data 
-Bootstrapping with replacement for chance eigen values 
-Temporal shuffling for chance prediction

Modelling:
-Poisson Spike Generation with time dependent and time independent firing rate
-Spike Trigerred Average 
-PCA
-dPCA
-TCA 

Statistical Analysis:
-Kruskal Wallis test p value by group - box plot 
